rc=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f832dd253f182d03a9b1c4c37588734b96854228","tid":669497,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T17:59:17.000Z","msg":"其實要第三方國家批准<br />\n<br />\n個原因是因為 <br />\n要滿足第三方國家的反壟斷法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(係當地有生意)<br />\n<br />\nQualcomm收購NXP 新聞講要九個國家監管部門同意  <br />\n個背後原理是咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73c2ac580d034bec6b268932b76ec2946c57a1da","tid":669497,"uid":122377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f832dd253f182d03a9b1c4c37588734b96854228","tid":669497,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T17:59:17.000Z","msg":"其實要第三方國家批准<br />\n<br />\n個原因是因為 <br />\n要滿足第三方國家的反壟斷法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(係當地有生意)<br />\n<br />\nQualcomm收購NXP 新聞講要九個國家監管部門同意  <br />\n個背後原理是咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T18:18:39.000Z","msg":"唔想獨大 壟斷掛"},{"pid":"b70b6cd5818e69a60491cb6d1e8eb7bd322e0586","tid":669497,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T23:46:10.000Z","msg":"大陸狗呢d不真不實 斯斯縮縮對事態度<br />\n美國佬會信先奇<br />\n將&quot;反口&quot;變成自己講數既籌碼  <br />\n Fool me once, shame on you. Fool me twice, shame on me<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f5ab73fa6f0619058107bd1501ee8c9d1368f7f","tid":669497,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T23:51:24.000Z","msg":"明明就係怕撚左美國先鬆手批准<br />\n仲講到自己好似有籌碼係手咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n華媒真係好撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"159404a55d2cd360f833506fa2e5d42f74233f4a","tid":669497,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73c2ac58